snippet.title: The Sims 4 Parenthood: Parenting Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Level up your Sim’s parenting skills to better satisfy child needs and influence their behaviors. The decisions you make influence how your Sim parents and leave a lasting impact on their child’s future. 

Learn more about this Game Pack: http://x.ea.com/30907 
What kind of parent will you be? Take the quiz: http://x.ea.com/30906
